Program: Thinking Allowed
Title: Exhaustion
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b08yq2bj
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 31 Jul 2017
Exhaustion: is extreme fatigue a peculiarly modern phenomenon? Laurie Taylor talks to Ann Katharina Schaffner, Reader in Comparative Literature and Medical Humanities at the University of Kent and author of a multi disciplinary study into weariness, past and present. Also, listeners' thoughts on subway travel. Producer:Jayne Egerton. Show less